<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, November 21 (Xinhua) -- The Romanian police have
once again tapped into a uranium smuggling ring and seized 380
grams of uranium-235 in the country's capital of Bucharest, the
national TV reported Friday.
</P>
