<HEADLINE> Industrial Sales by Provincial Regions on Fast Growth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 22 (Xinhua) -- The latest statistics from
State Statistical Bureau show that all the provinces,
municipalities and autonomous regions generated 453.7 billion yuan
in industrial output last September, a year-on-year increase of
13.18 percent.
</P>
<P>
The top three manufacturers were Jiangsu, Shandong and Shanghai, of
which the sales stood at 57.9 billion yuan, 38.5 billion yuan and
34 billion yuan, respectively.  
</P>
</TEXT>
